snippet.title: corru.observer EP0 Playthrough
snippet.description:
corru.observer is a relatively new site/game I recently found out about, this is a playthrough of its first available episode.
It's still in development, yet it has managed to grab my attention and make me invested in its story.

You can play it here: https://corru.observer/
Developer's website: https://corru.works/

Unofficial discord server: https://discord.gg/2FZeb3VTmV
